      "contents": "<div class=\"markitup-box\">\n\t\t\t朝鲜领导人金正恩周一表示，应在《宪法》中将韩国定义为“头号敌国”和“永远的主敌”，并写入“在战时完全占领、平定、收复大韩民国”的内容。韩国总统尹锡悦周二(1月16日)强硬回应称，韩国现届政府与历届政府都不同，一旦朝鲜发起挑衅，韩方将“加倍反制”。<a href=\"url/link/aHR0cHM6Ly93d3cudm9hY2hpbmVzZS5jb20vYS9zb3V0aC1rb3JlYS1hbmQtbm9ydGgta29yZWEtbGVhZGVycy1lbmdhZ2Utd2FyLW9mLXdvcmRzLTIwMjQwMTE2Lzc0NDE3NDcuaHRtbA\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://www.voachinese.com/a/south-korea-and-north-korea-leaders-engage-war-of-words-20240116/7441747.html\">https://www.voachinese.com/a/south-korea-and-north-korea-leaders-engage-war-of-words-20240116/7441747.html</a> </div>",
